        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事Barr認為司法部調查是對央行獨立性的「攻擊」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"聯儲會理事Barr認為司法部調查是對央行獨立性的「攻擊」\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RKswiYa390hCjY0BYCXiGA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/b8eda360-f25c-11f0-ad3f-eadbad085ddc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聯儲會理事Barr認為司法部調查是對央行獨立性的「攻擊」</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
